Package com._360t.structured.model.template

Interface MessageModel

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    CompleteMessage, ReceiveMessage, SendMessage
    public interface MessageModel

    Define the structure of the message model

    This interface is used to define basic properties of every concrete message object by the help of get and set methods. With the help of this interface, the message is defined as an concrete class that has several special fields and allows the property of a message to be separated and concat each other whenever it needs.
